---
import V3InteriorLayout from '../../../layouts/V3InteriorLayout.astro';
---

<V3InteriorLayout
  title="Greenvalley - Opening the 17th Anniversary"
  eyebrow="Set story"
  description="Maya Fourteen opens Greenvalley's 17th anniversary: a 90-minute sunset session at the club voted World's #1 by DJ Mag five times, before Beltran, Michael Bibi and Chemical Surf."
  heroImage="/images/video-hero-greenvalley.webp"
  heroImageCredit
  heroImageAlt="Maya Fourteen performing at Greenvalley, Brazil"
  hasEsSibling
>
  <div class="video-frame">
    <iframe
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mWqUmkWs3wY"
      title="Empty to Full Dancefloor: Sunset DJ Set at Greenvalley | Maya Fourteen"
      loading="lazy"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
      allowfullscreen
    ></iframe>
  </div>

  <p>
    The dancefloor was empty when it started. The sun was still high, thousands were on their
    way, and the assignment was as clear as it was unforgiving: open the 17th anniversary of
    Greenvalley, voted World's #1 Club by DJ Mag five times, and build the energy that
    Beltran, Michael Bibi and Chemical Surf would carry through the night.
  </p>
  <p>
    It was Greenvalley's first sunset session in over a decade. The set was designed as a pure
    progression, the long burn: organic textures and tribal warmth first, then melodic deep
    house, finally deep tech and tech house grooves, letting the energy grow naturally as the
    crowd arrived. Ninety minutes, empty to full.
  </p>
  <p class="venue-note">
    Greenvalley, Camboriú, Santa Catarina, Brazil. Five times voted World's #1 Club by DJ Mag,
    fifteen consecutive years on the DJ Mag podium, and a pilgrimage site for electronic music
    fans worldwide.
  </p>

  <h2>The journey</h2>

  <h3>Opening: organic and melodic foundations</h3>
  <ul class="tracklist">
    <li><span class="ts">00:00</span>Cruz Vittor, Nacho Varela, Nauel - Underworld (Volen Sentir Remix)</li>
    <li><span class="ts">07:10</span>Dave Seaman - Rapscallion's Revenge (Original 12" Mix)</li>
    <li><span class="ts">13:30</span>Davi - Lie Machine</li>
    <li><span class="ts">19:40</span>Samu.l - Have It Like That</li>
    <li><span class="ts">27:05</span>PillowTalk &amp; Gustavo Lobo - Gonna Be With You (Kellerkind Remix)</li>
    <li><span class="ts">33:10</span>Manuel Kane &amp; Kiki Botonaki - We Fly (Christos Fourkis Remix)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Transition: deep house and progressive builds</h3>
  <ul class="tracklist">
    <li><span class="ts">40:00</span>WiLDKATS - Perpetrating</li>
    <li><span class="ts">45:45</span>Maya Fourteen - Uniqueness feat. Francesca <span class="note">· her release on Systematic Recordings</span></li>
    <li><span class="ts">52:00</span>Alexey Union &amp; Anturage - Visions</li>
    <li><span class="ts">57:55</span>Helsloot - Disco Maxi</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Peak: deep tech and tech house energy</h3>
  <ul class="tracklist">
    <li><span class="ts">1:03:51</span>Rex the Dog - Change This Pain For Ecstasy</li>
    <li><span class="ts">1:11:54</span>German Brigante - You Know</li>
    <li><span class="ts">1:17:26</span>Mike Tohr - Whales (Extended Mix)</li>
    <li><span class="ts">1:22:02</span>Nick Curly - Squid</li>
    <li><span class="ts">1:28:20</span>Ost &amp; Kjex - Kaputt (Karmon Remix)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Bonus track</h3>
  <ul class="tracklist">
    <li><span class="ts">1:34:20</span>Mario Franca &amp; Maya Fourteen - Feel Better <span class="note">· her release on VIVa MUSiC</span></li>
  </ul>

  <a class="cta-button" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mWqUmkWs3wY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch the full set on YouTube</a>
</V3InteriorLayout>

<style>
  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .video-frame iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  p {
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .venue-note {
    font-size: 0.88em;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-size: 1.35em;
    margin: 1.6em 0 0.3em;
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 0.78em;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin: 1.4em 0 0.4em;
  }

  .tracklist {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 0.88em;
    line-height: 1.9;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .tracklist:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .ts {
    display: inline-block;
    min-width: 4.4em;
    opacity: 0.55;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .note {
    opacity: 0.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    p {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
